### ── FAVORITES SERVICE (/favorites) ────────────────────────────────────────
### Environment: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev

### 1. Add to favorites — Customer Bauer, Porsche 911
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites/addFavorite
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000005"
}

### 2. Add to favorites — Customer Bauer, Tesla Model Y
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites/addFavorite
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000025"
}

### 3. List favorites — via entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/Favorites
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 4. List favorites — via function
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/listFavorites()
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 5. Add same vehicle again — should be rejected (duplicate)
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites/addFavorite
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000005"
}

### 6. Remove from favorites — Porsche 911
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites/removeFavorite
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000005"
}

### 7. Favorites list — Porsche 911 should no longer be present
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/listFavorites()
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 8. View Customer Hoffmann's favorites — should be rejected
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/Favorites
Authorization: {{customerHoffmannAuth}}
